DESCRIPTION:Join us for an immersive Fungi Walk with Mamlakatoi as we explore the hidden world of mushrooms\, mycelium\, and forest decomposers. Led by a nature guide\, you'll learn to spot fungi species\, understand their vital role in our ecosystem\, and discover the magic right beneath your feet.\n\nThis programme is in conjunction with MAP’s ongoing exhibition\, Paper Gardens: Art\, Botany and Empire.
DTEND:20260531T060000Z
